  <thing id="sSorConPla" name="Control Plants" description="This spell enables you to control the actions of one or more plant creatures {b}(up to 2 HD/level of plant creatures, no two of which can be more than 30 ft. apart){/b} for a short period of time. You command the creatures by voice and they understand you, no matter what language you speak. Even if vocal communication is impossible (in the area of a {i}silence{/i} spell, for instance), the controlled plants do not attack you. At the end of the spell, the subjects revert to their normal behavior.\n\nSuicidal or self-destructive commands are simply ignored." compset="Spell" summary="Control actions of one or more plant creatures.">
