Dragon Compendium page 171

Poison Vials contain 1 dose of poison only, the charges do not stack add individual vials singularly!

*Note*
In accordance with Primary and secondary source plus FAQ's Text trumps table has been used.

The Dragon Compendium table contains a number of mistakes regarding the Toxins of Cerilon article.

Added by Bodrin]]></comment>
